Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your headband is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, Mr. Liebert, who emigrated\Nfrom East to West Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appeared before the media with his wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieberts showed no signs of exhaustion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they, along with their fraternal\Ntwins, a son and a daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,smiled brightly at the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Liebert, any opinions about the West?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's difficult to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... now that I can freely express myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the words to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, the answer to that question...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lies in the smiles of my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that your children are\Nfully enjoying their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, would you tell us how things really are in the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! An acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, show me both of your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I would've been right either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because all the acorns here are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, brother! Did you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the city from the car on our way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely different from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of pretty stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of different clothes and toys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you saw them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all yours too, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they all mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you on TV, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I wonder if someone's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... do this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Uncle Josef and Aunt Klara died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mr. Bodecker died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a monster came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed them all, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster came to take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you shoot, wipe the gun with a cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and throw it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you shoot me in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you shoot me, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, so the monster won't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone came...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone came to that mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who came?! Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A monster came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.05,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(221,200)\pos(362,353)}That Night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this mansion catch fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was supposed to be living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it might've been arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Wolf is asking to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General... Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, you were summoned\Nas well, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm waiting at the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just getting to this hospital here in\NPrague took everything I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you also received a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, only Johan sends letters to the man named Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bom into a military family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was guaranteed the path of the chosen at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only one who knows me\Nfor what I am is that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Red Rose Mansion burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're going to emerge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into broad daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who had their names\Ntaken from them, like myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to determine the cause of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it started in the second floor hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from how severely it burned in that area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could've been kerosene or gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was arson...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know for sure until we investigate further, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are signs that a wall in the\Nhallway had been torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw something at the base of the rose\Nbushes, so we started digging, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bones keep appearing, one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all these years, they'll finally see the light of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no one still alive who knows their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burned down to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion was our only clue to Tenma's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way! Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please contact headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A massive number of human bones were...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty-six people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1981...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forty-six people suddenly disappeared in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the little information I was able\Nto obtain in East Germany at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a certain experiment was being\Nconducted at that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only a theory, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that child was probably born there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are we going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And something warm to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Johan. It is a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children didn't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps when I gave him the name Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something inside of him awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in talking about the past anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about the future, and what will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I no longer have a future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann is with someone from our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our organization was unified by four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor G{\fnMeiryo U}ö{\fnNarkisim}derich, who was killed, and myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Eva is with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to use her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not let them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I live or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not able to stop them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to go berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save them, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmut Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, those who knew me as Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the proof of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Helmut Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what Johan saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world without names...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gates are locked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police must've made this place off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lipsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this place is important to you because of\Nthe book readings when you were a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place must have been important to you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might've been the trigger to recalling\Nyour memories, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and piled on top of each other in\Nthe great hall of this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since the visions you saw were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they found the remains of forty-six\Npeople at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was just as your brother, Johan, told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Johan see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it something horrifying, beyond all imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been there at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would l have been the one to become the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be for the best that this place burned down, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't be able to continue\Nliving if I lost this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because this place is full of sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't an excellent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't meet his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd been able to meet his expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But reality wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became an unwanted child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mom and dad, Mr. Lipsky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never lived with them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nina's memories do come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're happy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy memories..?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happy memories are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that if you don't have any happy memories,\Nyou can just make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma said you can just make them from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter, your mouth is covered in ketchup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is yours, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm creating a new puppet show right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of puppet show is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever wanted to see my puppet shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think people will like this next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see! I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl who lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have dreams that I'm being chased by a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have dreams that I'm chasing after a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will have wonderful dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, those dreams will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of what should come after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this girl's story have a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make it a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make it a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl decided to embark on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know what kind of journey it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the girl will stay strong and continue her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl looks back and waves many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in search of a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, you've come...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Mr. Lipsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the son of Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the owner of the Red Rose Mansion, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.82,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
